---
// About.astro — Devon + Reality Knights origin story
---

<section class="py-24 px-6" id="about">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <div class="mb-14">
      <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-3 font-medium">
        The person behind it
      </p>
      <h2
        class="font-outfit text-rk-text leading-tight"
        style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 700;"
      >
        Devon Lambert
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">

      <!-- Bio block -->
      <div class="about-block">
        <div class="about-accent-bar" style="background: #06B6D4;"></div>
        <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 1.05rem;">
          Devon Lambert started gaming at 8 years old on a NES and never really stopped.
          He's completed the entire Final Fantasy franchise, gone deep on Bleach, DBZ, and
          Demon Slayer — and at some point started practicing breathing techniques from the latter.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Philosophy block -->
      <div class="about-block">
        <div class="about-accent-bar" style="background: #7C3AED;"></div>
        <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 1.05rem;">
          Reality Knights is the holding company for what happens when someone like that
          also gets serious about markets, AI, and building things people actually want.
          Each venture starts with conviction — a clear problem, a real audience, and a
          reason to exist.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Origin story block — full width -->
      <div class="about-block about-block--full">
        <div class="origin-card">
          <span class="origin-label">Origin</span>
          <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 1.05rem;">
            The name goes back further than the business. Reality Knights started as a
            content crew — Devon and a friend making video content with a simple tagline:
            <em class="text-rk-glow font-medium not-italic">"Reality Knights because Reality Bites."</em>
            A nod to nightlife, a claim to being gentlemen about it. The name stuck.
            The ambition grew.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-block--full {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .about-accent-bar {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .origin-card {
    position: relative;
    background: #13131C;
    border: 1px solid #1E1E2E;
    border-left: 3px solid #7C3AED;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .origin-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7C3AED;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
